# Lab directories: auto-ignore extensionless binaries.
# Linux executables have no extension; source/doc files always do.
# Ignore everything inside Lab*/ that lacks a dot, whitelist the rest.
Lab*/**
!Lab*/**/
!Lab*/**/*.*
!Lab*/**/makefile
!Lab*/**/Makefile

# Build artifacts (placed AFTER the whitelist so they override it)
*.o
*.exe
a.out
